   "source": [
    "### Feature Engineering (RFM Analysis)\n",
    "### Transactional data needs to be aggregated to the customer level before applying most ML algorithms. We will calculate Recency (days since last purchase), Frequency (number of transactions), and Monetary (total spent)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 18,
   "id": "40ee9bc9-7632-4e26-ac2b-790d35014d12",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "RFM DataFrame:\n"
     ]
    },
    {
