   "source": [
    "### Unsupervised ML - K-Means Clustering\n",
    "### We will group similar customers together. First, we scale the data to ensure K-Means treats all features equally."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 19,
   "id": "48362955-9d24-47c5-baf5-0c69c24a69bb",
