    "### Prepare Data for Supervised ML\n",
    "### Now, let's create a prediction task: Can we predict if a customer will be a High-Value Customer? \n",
    "### Let's label the top 25% of spenders as 1 (High Value) and the rest as 0. We will use Recency and Frequency to predict this."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 23,
   "id": "d47deec3-7634-4ac5-a854-a8caad324637",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
